<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://wordnet.princeton.edu/perl/webwn?s=Progressive+tax" class="external text" title="http://wordnet.princeton.edu/perl/webwn?s=Progressive+tax" rel="nofollow">Princeton University WordNet</a>: (n) progressive tax (any tax in which the rate increases as the amount subject to taxation increases)</li>
